Sharding-JDBC of ShardingSphere is a JDBC extension;
Sharding-Proxy of ShardingSphere is a MySQL/PostgreSQL proxy.

Auto create tables is not ShardingSphere's scope, it should be do at orm or other database framework. ShardingSphere is a driver layer, do not focus user's business logic.

